reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Finally, the perfect minimalist shoe rack!
reviews.reviewText: If you are looking for easy assembling, adjustability, and a minimalist design, this shoe rack is it! I've searched through Amazon, all of the brands like West Elm, Pottery Barn, Target, etc. and ultimately landed on this very simple, design. It matched perfectly with our current furniture.The shoe rack is very sturdy. For use, there are 3 pairs on top and 3 pairs below. I couldn't be happier.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The shoe rack came in early today and was easy to assemble. Fits perfect in my closet with space to spare. I hate clutter and found this rack to be perfect for my eight pairs of shoes. Makes a big difference in closet appearance and selecting which pair to put on.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 3, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for lighter use
reviews.reviewText: This shoe rack is exactly what I was looking for. I wanted something that was minimalist in appearance (not an eyesore, like soooo many other shoe racks) that I could put by my back door for flip flops and those quick shoes that you throw on to step outside for a sec. Of course it isn’t as sturdy as wooden shoe racks, such as the bamboo kind, but for what I want, it’s exact. (I wouldn’t want this for my closet, to store 10 pairs of shoes, but I also wouldn’t want THAT kind of shoe rack to sit out.) This rack is well made and super easy to assemble. Minimalist packaging too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 2, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Size and adjustability
reviews.reviewText: I have a wooden bench in my foyer area, which is black wood, Farmhouse Decor. The lid opens up so you may place itens inside but I do not like my shoes to get dirty from other shoes. I looked everywhere for this exact measurement and it is perfect!!!! I can store 8 pairs of shoes altogether under my bench! This size is very hard to find, it is adjustable and I only used one rack. Heavy black metal, very durable and super easy to assemble!! Thank you so much!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Practical and sleek
reviews.reviewText: Love this shoe rack! I don't have an entryway in my apartment/there isn't much storage space near the door. I had a plastic mat for shoes and put this rack on top of it. I now have more storage for my shoes and for guests' without taking up any more space than before. It makes me feel more organized. Very happy with this purchase!

Easy and quick to assemble, plus it looks great in the entryway. I live in a one-room apartment, so the entryway is tight. This fits right in and is easy to match with the rest of your interior due to it's minimalistic design. Should you need to put more shoes on the rack, or have guests over, you can easily extend the shoerack as well.
